data.description:
Location, location, location! This townhome is close to shopping, restaurants, highways and parks. Updates include new carpet
throughout, new wood laminate flooring throughout the main level, new stove, microwave and refrigerator. Home has also been freshly
painted top to bottom. The open floor plan is great for entertaining and the kitchen features a raised counter for bar seating. The living
room features a cozy gas fireplace and a patio door that walks out to your private patio. The association area offers a large open area
with a playground, perfect for outdoor activities and gatherings.
